{"tid":977372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最低工資$37.5五一生效　增幅8.7%","createTime":"2019-01-11T06:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T08:12:13.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"440c67f091c0b377999aabd463db566c64c0b056","tid":977372,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190111/s00001/5402aeeac47118ef8916053684f94130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190111%2Fs00001%2F5402aeeac47118ef8916053684f94130.jpg&h=22f93107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首會同行政會議接納最低工資委員會的建議，將法定最低工資水平上調至每小時37.5元，比目前最低工資多3元，增幅8.7%。相關的《2019年最低工資條例（修訂附表3）公告》將於下周五（18日）刊憲，本月23日提交立法會；獲通過後，新最低工資將於5月1日起實施。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府下周五亦會就修訂記錄總工作時數的每月金額上限，將《2019年僱傭條例（修訂附表9）公告》刊憲，同樣本月23日提交立法會，獲通過後於5月1日生效。新公告規定，如僱主須就某工資期支付予僱員的工資款額，不低於每月15,300元，即可獲豁免記錄有關僱員於該工資期的總工作時數。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190111/s00001/1547188174002/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190111%2Fs00001%2F1547188174002%2F&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=559f6b7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190111%2Fs00001%2F1547188174002%2F&h=01f3563b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190111/s00001/1547188174002/</a>"},{"pid":"87d070045da60a08d4ae7579d12bd6f58f7490df","tid":977372,"uid":121580,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:52:10.000Z","msg":"肯定有中小企又話會頂唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f317a5102d0b31740cd55a7a6e589d9db42767","tid":977372,"uid":19454,"like":68,"dislike":7,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:53:16.000Z","msg":"一味加大銀碼有鬼用，d嘢一樣貴返，等於冇加過"},{"pid":"8b073d5377696fcf5d6831c11d7bb2d975d03cad",